<span id="freeTextContainer3374725080847042238">This book (written in the 80s) was clearly not intended to be read by Afghans or other persons of color. His descriptions of things &quot;all Afghans&quot; wore or did made me yawn and his portrayal of Jane made me cringe. This is a formulaic spy novel with awkward sex scenes set in Afghanistan. <br/><br/>There was a real shortage of books on Afghanistan in the 80s. That&apos;s been rectified. Skip this and read #ownvoices. </span>
