<span id="freeTextContainer8686849508087606642">I think it is worth reading as it was well researched for the background of the Russian involvement in Afghanistan, bearing in mind written long before recent events. There is a bibliography in the book for guidance to more in depth reading aboit Afghanistan.</span>

