<div id="review_1181802519" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1181802519" />
    <a title="David Jarrett" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4560356-david-jarrett"><img alt="David Jarrett" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1506615185p2/4560356.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1181802519?book_show_action=true">Jan 26, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="David Jarrett" class="user" itemprop="url" name="David Jarrett" href="/user/show/4560356-david-jarrett">David Jarrett</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780688058913" href="/book/show/2042501.Lie_Down_with_Lions">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1181802519" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6063924576219590126">For someone considered a master at his trade, Follett did not do so well with this book. None of the characters were likeable, the plot was weak, and I was glad when I reached the underwhelming conclusion.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


